rows.label: tlk42100152_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Ugh, how awful! I'm all
sticky with machine oil!

rows.label: tlk42100152_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Just by squeezing through a small
gap in the machinery, I got covered
in oil. Isn't that terrible?

rows.label: tlk42100152_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Now my proud coat is all matted
and flat, and it smells awful!

rows.label: tlk42100152_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Are you worried about me?
Thanks! I'll be fine once I
wash it off in the hot spring.

rows.label: tlk42100152_01_msg0005
rows.name:
It's super fun to go for a swim when
there are no people around! This is
a secret from the humans, okay?
